the leisure class is a 2015 comedy film by hbo films about a man who is trying to marry into a wealthy family and his unpredictable brother .   the film was directed by project greenlight season 4 contest winner , jason mann .   it is based on a 2012 short film written by mann that premiered at the 2013 raindance film festival .   season 4 of project greenlight aired on hbo as a documentary series chronicling the selection of mann and the production of the film .   the film premiered in los angeles in august 2015 and aired on hbo on november 2 , 2015 .